<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>32-708</num>
  <heading>Recordkeeping requirements.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall maintain adequate records of declarations of domestic partnership, termination statements, and amendments to declarations of domestic partnership and termination statements.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>The Mayor shall report annually to the Council on the number of domestic partnerships declared and terminated, including those terminated under section 3(d)(5).</text>
  </para>
